"Next, add a *Label* as a child of *Retry* and give it the *Text* \"Press "
"Enter to retry.\""
msgstr ""
"接下来，添加一个 *Label* 作为 *Retry* 的子项，将其 *Text* 设为“Press Enter "
"to retry.”（按回车键重试。）"

