"Click the *Other Node* button to create an *AudioStreamPlayer* and rename it "
"to *MusicPlayer*."
msgstr ""
"单击\\ *其他节点*\\ 按钮，创建一个 *AudioStreamPlayer* 然后将其重命名为 "
"*MusicPlayer*\\ （音乐播放器）。"

