"We have to register it as an autoload. Head to the *Project -> Project "
"Settings…* menu and click on the *Autoload* tab."
msgstr ""
"我们需要将其注册为自动加载。前往菜单\\ *项目 -> 项目设置...*\\ ，然后单击\\ *"
